write a shell program to read command line argument a number and print your name according to that number.

nano 

if [ $# -eq 0 ]; then
  echo "2"
  exit 1
fi

name="Madala Vijay Sai"

for ((i=1;i<=$1;i++)); do
  echo "$name"
done

e1.sh

